{"tid":912850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「功課已做」Trump：「我清楚掌握每個環節和每項法令，我比任何人都更清楚，我的本能是不會錯的」","createTime":"2018-11-23T03:43:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T04:07:59.000Z","uid":33307,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"15db6e8a65c3b1f3186be1616eadcd579e82f36b","tid":912850,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T03:43:00.000Z","msg":"My friend President Xi 又黎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n特朗普:與習近平G20會晤冀達貿協<br />\n<br />\n中美元首下周在阿根廷舉行的二十國集團(G20)峰會期間會晤，美國總統特朗普表示，期望與中國國家主席習近平會面時，能與北京政府達成貿易協議。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普周四在佛羅里達州向派駐海外的美軍，發表感恩節電話慰問，他其後召開記者會，表示已經為「特習會」充分做好準備，「我清楚掌握每個環節和每項法令，我比任何人都更清楚，我的本能是不會錯的」，特朗普這樣形容他為中美元首會晤所做的準備功夫。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普又稱，中國想達成貿易協議，美國在可行的情況下，也樂意達成協議。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普又重提他與習近平的關係，「我很喜歡他，我想他也喜歡我。不過，在我們推出一些政策後，可能他沒有像以前那樣喜歡我」。<br />\n<br />\nG20峰會將於11月30日至12月1日在布宜諾斯艾利斯舉行。<br />\n<br />\n另外，特朗普警告，若果來自墨西哥的中美洲移民問題惡化，不排除會全面關閉美國與墨西哥邊境，屆時美墨的貿易將會受損，在墨西哥製造的車輛，將不能輸入美國。"},{"pid":"5eadf630c6bee7a04f8411a0e8d36377e40b63a9","tid":912850,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T03:46:51.000Z","msg":"又撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e9087a372a8795ed6a86cc4ceb5db2e929b332c","tid":912850,"uid":179908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T03:50:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我很喜歡他，我想他也喜歡我</blockquote><br />\ngay<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1a06856a4156718112c9292dbca66edd46656e7","tid":912850,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5eadf630c6bee7a04f8411a0e8d36377e40b63a9","tid":912850,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T03:46:51.000Z","msg":"又撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:03:44.000Z","msg":"my friend<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e476b70838cc5183d07f65040021b6b619298372","tid":912850,"uid":147367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:05:16.000Z","msg":"若即若離，溝女高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e73f01528da6f4602fdaee50e526280776ea4c1","tid":912850,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e476b70838cc5183d07f65040021b6b619298372","tid":912850,"uid":147367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:05:16.000Z","msg":"若即若離，溝女高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:07:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}